Sec. 78.016. HEARING. At a hearing required by Section 78.014
of this code, a person whose land is included in or may be affected
by the proposed district may appear before the commissioners court
and testify for or against the creation of the district. If the
hearing lasts longer than one day, the commissioners court may
adjourn the hearing to another day.

Statute text rendered on: 8/6/2022

